Arugula Salad with Lemon Vinaigrette

10 min
$10
150 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeLow-Calorie

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Salad

Tags:

SaladQuickHealthy

Description

A refreshing and zesty salad that's perfect for a light meal or side dish!

Ingredients

  • arugula: 4 cups
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup
  • parmesan cheese: 1/4 cup
  • olive oil: 3 tablespoons
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
